caption: With a quite humble entrance, the moment you enter you will discover one of the most unique and beautiful synagogues in Paris. Shabbat Prayers are traditional Sephardic. The Community is cohesive and the Rabbi is very welcoming. He invited me for a shabbat dinner that was magnificent.
